Package: dprocsim
Type: Package
Title: Distribution Estimation Accounting for Prior Uncertainty in a Bayesian Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sam", "Tyner", email = "sctyner90@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Simulate distribution functions from Dirichlet Process priors 
    when the distribution of data is unknown. Then, using the conjugacy
    of the DPP, simulate from the posterior after obtaining data. Finally, 
    approximate the posterior density with intervals around values in the range. 
License: GPL-2
